title: [Feature Request] Math examples
body: Examples such as visualizations and calculations would be helpful

title: [Wiki Addition] Documentation of existing scripts
body: The existing scripts need to be documented well so new users can understand how to use them

title: [Wiki Addition] Coding resources page
body: A page that lists out resources that would help with learning to code in case the provided scripts are not enough would be well recieved

title: [Feature Request] Liquid interaction
body: Mixing two liquids together for a reaction would allow the creation of a large variety of chemistry equations

title: [Improvement] Add more examples to the chemistry scene
[Feature Request] WebVR version
body: A WebVR branch using Mozilla's webVR export would be nice (https://github.com/mozilla/unity-webvr-export)

title: [Feature Request] Better 2D version
body: The 2D version could be significantly improved

title: [Feature Request] Windows for the classroom
body: Transparent windows would help with making the environment feel less claustrophobic

title: [Feature Request] Physics example level
body: A physics example level that shows how to setup Unity physics with many examples would be helpful

title: [Feature Request] More 3D models for lesson creation
body: Specific asset packs for subjects will be helpful for creating lessons in different subjects, such as chemistry models, biology models, physics models
